text: Greetings from Asbury Park, N.J. is the debut studio album by Bruce Springsteen. It was released on 5 January, 1973 through Columbia Records and went to number 60 in the United States, number 35 in Sweden and number 41 in the United Kingdom when it charted in 1985. It was ranked #379 on the Rolling Stone 500 Greatest Albums of all time in 2003. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1973 albums Category:Debut albums Category:Bruce Springsteen albums Category:Columbia Records albums
